CHALLENGE 3: Create MongodB Atlas account and play with demo data

Find all restaurants of cuisine American and return only their address

{cuisine: "American", borough : "Brooklyn"},{address: 1}  //in atlas it should be inside PROJECT field in options
{cuisine: "American", borough : "Brooklyn"}.limit(2) 

with a coma in between the arguments by default is AND, if you want OR you must add in front
{$or [{cuisine: "American", borough : "Brooklyn"}]}

find airbnbs in portugal
{"address.country" : "Portugal"} //when nested object field, use quotes!
xxxx.count() returns number of results matching your query


More restaurant related exercises: 
https://www.w3resource.com/mongodb-exercises/
